Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.74,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ここは僕らの戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:03.55,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}少し先の理想すら追えない{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:06.96,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉 一つのみ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.29,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 そっと閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:15.19,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}今はただ 振動に応えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:18.24,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}心の瞳(め)で Lock-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.99,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}君が叫ぶ Push up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:25.70,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}この痛みと熱さが答だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.01,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-キミハマダ戦エル-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}幻聴か?否か?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:37.33,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}<回路=意識>(カイロ)を意思で導け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:42.59,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}決してのみ込まれるな 無限の谷へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.35,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}目の前の不条理を壊せ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.93,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Comment: 1,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.47,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}You just call up circuit zone!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.31,0:00:55.97,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}"思緒"擾亂心中平靜
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.74,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這裡是我們的戰場
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.81,0:01:03.55,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}連眼前的理想都無法追尋{\fsp1}…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.31,0:01:06.96,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言語 嚥回腹中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.29,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 鎖在心裡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.41,0:01:15.19,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}如今只要 回應這振動就好
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.08,0:01:18.24,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}睜開心眼 Lock-on!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.99,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}你在呼喊 Push up!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.57,0:01:25.70,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這痛楚和灼熱便是答案!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.39,0:01:29.01,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-你還能繼續戰鬥-
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.16,0:01:31.61,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這是幻聽嗎?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.61,0:01:37.33,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}意識 用意志來引導
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.43,0:01:42.59,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}謹記不要被吞入 那不見底的深淵
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.35,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}擊潰眼前的荒唐不經!
Comment: 1,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.93,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Can you break up endless war?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:13.22,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}見つめ合う  心  ひらいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:19.17,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}強がりと弱さのループ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:25.87,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ねえ少しは  慣れたはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:35.94,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言葉にしても全てのことは  わからないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:40.45,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}それだけは覚えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:43.66,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}こんなものじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}自分に気付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:54.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}勇気に乗せたなら  世界は変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:23:01.97,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}独りじゃ知らなかった  あのTELEPATHY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:08.44,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}導く  後ろ姿  とても眩しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:15.47,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}だから私は  目をそらさず君を見てる
